data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the heart of St. Paul. Upon entering the home, you are greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living room features large windows that allow natural light to flood the space, creating a bright and airy ambiance. The open floor plan seamlessly connects to the dinning area, providing an ideal layout for entertaining guests. The kitchen has open storage and pantry space. The main floor bedroom is large and has a walk in closet with big bright windows conveniently next to the bath. Upstairs, a bedroom and a sitting area with an abundant walk in closet await Travel downstairs and you will find the 2nd living area connected to a laundry corner and the 3rd bedroom. This bedroom has ample storage and an egress window that lets in plenty of light. You will also find the 2nd bath with a newer vanity. Outside the back door conveniently located off the kitchen is the back yard, Almost fully fenced with a storage shed.
